{'category': 'Notice', 'content': '<table style="width: 468.9pt; border-collapse: collapse; margin: auto auto auto 4.65pt"> \n <tbody> \n  <tr style="height: 59.05pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">岗位</span></b>\n    </div> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">类型</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)"><br> </span>\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">专职博士后&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)"><br> </span>\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 42.1pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">聘任</span></b>\n    </div> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">方式</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">学校经费聘任&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)"><br> </span>\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 28.5pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">岗位名称（从事专业）</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">食品科学与工程、纺织科学与工程、材料学</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 66pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">招聘人数</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">1</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 31.5pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">聘用期限</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">3年</span>\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 51pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">岗位职责</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">1、</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">完成岗位规定的科研工作任务，积极申报和参与国家级、省部级或横向科研项目。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">2</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">、</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt">积极参与创新平台建设，积极参加各种学术活动</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt">和</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt">国际交流。</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt"><br> </span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">3</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">、完成校院两级公共事务及其他人才培养任务。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">4</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">、承担校、院、系交办的其他工作。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">5</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">、完成岗位聘任合同中规定的其他工作。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     &nbsp;\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n  <tr style="height: 48.75pt"> \n   <td valign="middle" width="112" style="border-top: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 84pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt" align="center">\n     <b><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">招聘条件</span></b>\n    </div> </td> \n   <td valign="middle" width="513" style="border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1pt solid; width: 384.9pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: rgb(255,255,255) 31.875pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; background-color: transparent"> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">1</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">、热爱高等教育事业，思想品德好，具有良好的综合素质和职业道德。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">2</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">、基础知识和基本技能扎实，熟悉本学科前沿领域，有较高的科研能力和学术发展潜力。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">3、具有国内外高水平大学博士学位；原则上</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">应</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">具有1年及以上海外</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">学习或工作</span>\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">经历。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">4、勤于钻研，工作主动，具备良好的职业道德和严谨的教风、学风，有团队合作精神和独立开展科学研究的能力，已在国内外高水平期刊上发表论文。</span>\n    </div> \n    <div style="background: rgb(255,255,255); layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0pt; line-height: 20pt">\n     <span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(13,13,13)">5、身心健康，年龄不超过35岁。</span>&nbsp;\n    </div> \n    <div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt">\n     &nbsp;\n    </div> </td> \n  </tr> \n </tbody> \n</table> \n<div style="margin: 0pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">备注：符合国家博士后进站要求的专职博士后应同时申请国家博士后</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt">\n <b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">招聘程序</span></b>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">1.应聘人员登录四川大学人事信息管理系统（</span>\n <span style="font-size: 12pt">http://rsxxgl.scu.edu.cn/Common/Recruitment.aspx</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">），填写个人应聘申请；注册时请提供准确的个人信息，因个人信息不实造成的后果由应聘者本人承担。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">2.由单位招聘工作领导小组对应聘人员进行甄选，确定参加面试人员名单。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">3.由单位教授委员会专家和相关部处人员对候选人进行面试，择优确定拟聘人员。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">4.对拟聘人员进行体检、公示，无异议后上报学校。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">5.学校审批。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt">\n <b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">待遇:</span></b>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">按照四川大学相关规定执行。</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt">\n <b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0)">报名时间及联系方式:</span></b>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 28pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">1.报名时间：即日起-2016年</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">10</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">月</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">20</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">日</span>\n</div> \n<div style="margin: 0pt">\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">2.联系人： &nbsp;</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">李慧</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;联系电话：</span>\n <span style="font-size: 14pt">028-85461730</span>\n</div>', 'time': '2016-09-21T03:22:32Z', 'title': '四川大学轻纺与食品学院专职博士后岗位招聘启事', 'academy': '轻纺与食品学院', 'originURL': 'http://qfsp.scu.edu.cn/index.aspx?menuid=25&type=articleinfo&lanmuid=71&infoid=3842&language=cn'}